  "body": "# Problem\nNew app icon specification for Google Play\nApp icons on Google Play are changing. From June 24, transparent backgrounds will no longer be allowed, and Google Play will dynamically add rounded corners and drop shadows to icons.\n\nLet us know when your icon meets the new specification. If you're not quite ready, you can keep using the old specification for now. We'll automatically scale down your icon on June 24. \n\nhttps://developer.android.com/google-play/resources/icon-design-specifications\n\n![](https://user-images.githubusercontent.com/6584810/57029878-48b5e680-6c43-11e9-9a4d-6175f60c55e8.png)\n\n@hesterbruikman can you have a look if the new icon proposed in PlayStore is ok\n\n",
